Rating_Title: New Citroen C5 - Wait Is Finally Over
Reviews_Description: New Citroen C5 is launched today with lots of new features like drive display, 360 degree camera, dual climate control and more. I am really wanted to drive this car and see it's performance and mileage.

Rating_Title: Launched Today  - New Citroen C5 Aircross
Reviews_Description: Citroen C5 2022 will be launched today with new features. I am hoping the price range wouldn't be that high for this SUV. The New C5 Aircross looks more stylish & powerful than before. I am super excited to drive this SUV soon.
